songs.text: You started from the bottom, and now you're here.
You have a lot of enemies... Oh wait, I meant energy.
songs.emotion: You are great at hiding your emotions!

songs.text: You get emotional, but only if there are bands involved, or it's 6PM.
songs.emotion: You're wasting your relationship with a relationship.

songs.text: You make all the headlines, but are still trying to figure out the square root of 69.
songs.emotion: You're the type to go to the doctor when you have a broken heart.

songs.text: You get emotional, but that's from time to time.
songs.emotion: All these dictionaries, but you still couldn't keep your word.

songs.text: If you die, you are a legend.
songs.emotion: All these coins, but you stil couldn't change.

songs.text: Take care and find your love.
songs.emotion: All these games and you decided to play me.

songs.text: Preach, know yourself, and run through the six with your woes.
songs.emotion: Call me crazy... At least you're calling.

songs.text: You need some company. Hold on.
songs.emotion: No strings attached and you still got tied up in that.

songs.text: When a good thing goes bad, it's not the end of the world.
